description:
```      ✰ - ASTRAL EXPRESS ONLINE NETWORK - ✰               ```
> A.E.O.N, or Astral Express Online Network, is a formal collective network of several online communities relating to Honkai: Star Rail.

> Representatives from across all communities work together to interact with each other in order to exchange information and create a united network that strives for quality, safety, and strength in numbers by utilizing a common communication ground.

> If you are interested in joining us as a member with your server, want to know more about our collective, or just want to hang out with the leaders of your favorite HSR communities, feel free to visit our Discord server! 

----------★・    **JOIN US! - [ AEON DISCORD  SERVER](https://discord.gg/bAmwkDYZ5e)**・★----------
